<h3 id="how-to-install--configure-captive-portal-with-freeradius-with-pfsense-firewall">How to install &amp; Configure Captive Portal with FreeRadius with Pfsense Firewall</h3>

<h1 id="table-of-contents">Table of contents</h1>
<ol>
  <li><a href="#What-is-Captive-Portal?">What is Captive Portal?</a></li>
  <li><a href="#STEP-1:-Install-FreeRADIUS3-Package">STEP 1:- Install FreeRADIUS3 Package</a></li>
  <li><a href="#STEP-2:-Create-Server-certificate">STEP 2:- Create Server certificate</a></li>
  <li><a href="#STE-3:--Configure-FreeRadius-Server">STEP 3:- Configure FreeRadius Server</a></li>
