<h4 id="step-04--create-freeradius-users">STEP 04:- Create FreeRadius Users</h4>

<p>Navigate to  <strong>Services &gt; FreeRadius, Users</strong>  tab.<br />
<img src="/images/pages/pfsense_captive_portal/image021.png" width="100%" /></p>

<p>All the other settings can be change upon to your requirements.</p>

